metadata.name: Matrix Blind Box NFT
metadata.description: MatrixETF Blind Box is the first blind box NFT from MatrixETF, which reatively combine Farming, ETF Fund Right Certificate, Token Airdrop and NFT together in DeFi ecosystem. In addition it will bring users totally new experiences and new play methods as well as NFT value. There are several kinds of NFT in Matrix Blind Box which include Farming NFT, Fund Certificate NFT, Token Certificate NFT and Gold Membership NFT etc, each kind of NFT will have different type, rarity and right.
